T. 22 S., Rs. 64 and 65 E.;
T. 23 S., Rs. 64 and 65 E.;
T. 24 S., Rs. 64 and 65 E.;
T. 25 S., R. 65 E.
This order shall continue in full force and effect unless and until revoked by the President, or by act of Congress.
HERBERT HOOVER
The White House,
April 25, 1930.
